Class SelectiveBuilderFunction

java.lang.Object
io.github.ljnelson.oci.secrets.configsource.SelectiveBuilderFunction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Function<String,GetSecretBundleRequest.Builder>
public final class SelectiveBuilderFunction extends Object implements Function<String,GetSecretBundleRequest.Builder>
A decorator Function that guards another similar Function with a Predicate controlling when it will be executed.

  • Method Details

    • apply

      public final GetSecretBundleRequest.Builder apply(String propertyName)
      If the propertyNameValidator supplied at construction time returns true when supplied with the supplied propertyName, then the builderFunction supplied at construction time is executed with the same propertyName and its return value is returned.

      In all other cases this method returns null.

      Specified by:
      apply in interface Function<String,GetSecretBundleRequest.Builder>
      Parameters:
      propertyName - a MicroProfile Config property name; may be null
      Returns:
      a fully-configured GetSecretBundleRequest.Builder suitable for the supplied propertyName, or null
      See Also:
      • SelectiveBuilderFunction(Function, Predicate)
